Event data slice from ICEWS

Source: R/icews.R
icews.Rd

Event data from ICEWS for select countries from 2002 to 2014, and additional nodal variables from the World Bank and Polity IV.

Usage

data(icews)

Source

icews

References

add icews reference (icews)

Examples

data(icews)
icews[1:3,]
